{"id":26831,"date":"2020-04-01T14:53:58","date_gmt":"2020-04-01T18:53:58","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/anerdsworld.com\/?p=26831"},"modified":"2020-06-30T21:18:06","modified_gmt":"2020-07-01T01:18:06","slug":"navigating-through-covid-19","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/anerdsworld.com\/navigating-through-covid-19\/","title":{"rendered":"Navigating Through Covid"},"content":{"rendered":"<blockquote>\n<h3><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-26838 size-full\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" src=\"https:\/\/anerdsworld.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/Navigating-through-COVID19.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"668\" height=\"382\" srcset=\"https:\/\/anerdsworld.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/Navigating-through-COVID19.jpg 668w, https:\/\/anerdsworld.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/Navigating-through-COVID19-400x229.jpg 400w, https:\/\/anerdsworld.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/Navigating-through-COVID19-255x146.jpg 255w, https:\/\/anerdsworld.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/Navigating-through-COVID19-50x29.jpg 50w, https:\/\/anerdsworld.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/04\/Navigating-through-COVID19-131x75.jpg 131w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 668px) 100vw, 668px\" \/><\/h3>\n<\/blockquote>\n<p>For the continued safety and well-being of our nerds and customers, our head office and flagship store\u00a0will remain temporarily closed.<\/p>\n<p><b data-stringify-type=\"bold\">Fully Remote Workforce<\/b><\/p>\n<p>Our whole team is now required to work from home, and we&#8217;re using our internal communications tools such as Zoom, Slack, phone and email, to keep staff updated on the latest COVID-19 developments. We have a strong remote work culture \u2014 with over 30 specialists working full time remotely in Toronto \u2014 and that has helped us to quickly adapt. This has allowed us to continue to deliver undisrupted work and to support our customers and to remain fully focused on their important projects.<\/p>\n<p>We know that everybody\u2019s circumstances are different, and if you have suggestions for how we can better support you, please let us know by emailing\u00a0<a class=\"c-link\" href=\"mailto:nerd@anerdsworld.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" aria-describedby=\"slack-kit-tooltip\">nerd@anerdsworld.com<\/a>. Chris and I will read every email that we get. We promise to listen to your concerns, consider and discuss your feedback, and continually look for ways for all of us to navigate through this situation with empathy.<\/p>\n<p>For up-to date information from the City&#8217;s official website, please view the following link for details on COVID-19:\u00a0<a class=\"c-link\" href=\"https:\/\/slack-redir.net\/link?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.toronto.ca%2Fhome%2Fcovid-19%2F\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" aria-describedby=\"slack-kit-tooltip\">https:\/\/www.toronto.ca\/home\/covid-19\/<\/a><\/p>\n<p>Please remain safe and healthy during these difficult times,<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-26255\" src=\"https:\/\/anerdsworld.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/anw_signatures_grace.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"208\" height=\"80\" srcset=\"https:\/\/anerdsworld.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/anw_signatures_grace.png 1151w, https:\/\/anerdsworld.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/anw_signatures_grace-400x153.png 400w, https:\/\/anerdsworld.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/anw_signatures_grace-1024x392.png 1024w, https:\/\/anerdsworld.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/anw_signatures_grace-260x100.png 260w, https:\/\/anerdsworld.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/anw_signatures_grace-50x19.png 50w, https:\/\/anerdsworld.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/anw_signatures_grace-150x57.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 208px) 100vw, 208px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Grace\u00a0Hughes<span class=\"c-message__edited_label\" dir=\"ltr\" aria-describedby=\"slack-kit-tooltip\">\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>For the continued safety and well-being of our nerds and customers, our head office and flagship store\u00a0will remain temporarily closed. Fully Remote Workforce Our whole team is now required to work from home, and we&#8217;re using our internal communications tools&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":26832,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[1],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/anerdsworld.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/26831"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/anerdsworld.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/anerdsworld.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/anerdsworld.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/anerdsworld.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=26831"}],"version-history":[{"count":8,"href":"https:\/\/anerdsworld.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/26831\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":27540,"href":"https:\/\/anerdsworld.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/26831\/revisions\/27540"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/anerdsworld.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/26832"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/anerdsworld.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=26831"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/anerdsworld.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=26831"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/anerdsworld.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=26831"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}